				<h2 class="title icon icon0">
					Re: Google Researches Alternative Authentication Methods
				</h2>
				

						
						
				<div class="content">
					<div id="post_message_1769624">
						<blockquote class="postcontent restore ">
							The big issue with security is the password itself.   The very nature of just a password is weak as computing power grows and grows the common criminal will gain access to multiple arrays of Nvidia Tesla units that can do huge amounts of computing.   Causing a need for longer passwords.   The problem is we eventually hit a point beyond which a person can remember a truly secure password.<br />
<br />
2 factor is the future I think,  it will have to be because the lone password is no longer sustainable.
						</blockquote>
