		</div>
	</div>
</div>Yep, last pass rocks.  It is better than the other options as it is cross platform even on mobile and you can add a physical authenticator to it.  It makes life so much easier and more secure.  It is easily the best change I've made to my computing habits.  I was thinking about adding the google authenticator to it but I've read some people having issues with it if the app updates and the settings are forgotten.  I wish it was easier to use for video games such as my steam account or battle.net though.
						</blockquote>
					</div>

					
				</div>
